  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Controversial preacher's letter to President Ranil?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President's Media Unit has stated that there is no truth in the news that controversial preacher Nithyananda has written a letter to Sri Lankan President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "There were reports that Nithyananda was in need of medical help and sought asylum for that.",
        "Indian media reported that he also said in his letter that Kailash, the heavenly land where he lives, will accept all the medical expenses.",
        "At this stage no letters were received from Nithyananda. Also, the Presidential Media Unit said that there is no truth in this news. (R)"
      ],
